Leaves coriaceous, petiolate;
					blade narrowly oblong, 15-20 by 4-6 cm, apex acute, base cuneate;
					petiole 6-10 cm long, canaliculate, clasping the stem for up to 3/4 its circumference, not auriculate or decurrent.

