					lid orbicular, 2.5-3.5 by 2.25-3.25 cm, lower surface lacking appendages, nectar glands densely set near base of midrib, as lower pitcher.

Male inflorescence c. 25 cm long;
					peduncles c. 6 cm long, 2 mm diam. at base;
